---
description: Wrap an existing route's handler with a chi middleware (modify-aware generator, idempotent).
argument-hint: <METHOD> <path> <middleware-ref>
---
Run `gofasta g middleware $ARGUMENTS --dry-run --json` first. If
the generator reports `ROUTE_ALREADY_WRAPPED`, the middleware is
already applied — confirm with the user before re-running.
Otherwise apply the planned patch.
